title: [Wexna's Outfitting]
[Wexna's General Store]
description: Blue watered silk walls rise from a glossy mahogany floor.  Just above a woven Vornavian silk rug hangs a fused sun and moon wall-hanging, and a vaulted ceiling completes the picture.  A carved mahogany box and a large cherrywood cabinet stand side by side in the middle of the room.
